{"tid":559357,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★綜援唔夠使  學者轟政府金額低","createTime":"2018-02-13T06:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T11:48:21.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"088c878a486949ea6d0723298af2ffb4abf8c027","tid":559357,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:11:11.000Z","msg":"推行二十多年的綜合社會保障援助計劃（綜援），一直被指金額低，各項特別津貼及補助金亦無助應付受助人的基本生活開支。有學者昨在立法會福利事務委員會會議上，狠批政府計算綜援標準金額時以長者開支模式為主，<span style=\"color: red;\">對普通成人受助者明顯「唔夠使」</span>。綜援雖設租金津貼，但單靠津貼金額在市場上「直情搵唔到單位」。社會福利署回應，調整綜援金額時已參考統計處數字，認為是客觀計算。<br />\n<br />\n捍衞綜援權利大聯盟一行十三人昨在會前到政府總部請願，<span style=\"color: red;\">要求調高綜援金額</span>，取消長者六十五歲才可領綜援的措施，容許長者及殘疾人士以個人申請綜援。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180213/00176_030.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180213%2F00176_030.html&d=IC4%2BU%2FsjN3mjXxYTZGhUmIS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=4de4938d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180213/00176_030.html</a>"},{"pid":"f6f592ca4d456546118bd89d40ab9e4c662aaedc","tid":559357,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:11:27.000Z","msg":"too low<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0e2596b0ee16f7afd1fb56945260a20ab65691","tid":559357,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180213/photo/0213-00176-030b1.jpg?t=1518502324004\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180213%2Fphoto%2F0213-00176-030b1.jpg%3Ft%3D1518502324004&h=70a53949&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fbd419fc4e35ccbfd16c19893b7dd8965fe0011f","tid":559357,"uid":68094,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:12:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d00fad7f8dbdc3cd702909e416ac4e70178e63f0","tid":559357,"uid"